<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>post-build<sp/>command<sp/>will<sp/>have<sp/>deployed<sp/>the<sp/>Qt<sp/>DLLs<sp/>automatically.<sp/>For<sp/>example:</highlight></codeline>
